strings: <voice_0x01001CEA><se_high>Princess Medea: I'm so glad you're safe, <hero>!
<voice_0x01001CEB><se_high>Princess Medea: When you were captured, I didn't know what I was going to do.
<voice_0x01001CEC><se_high>Princess Medea: Father and I decided to continue the journey by ourselves...
<voice_0x01001CED><se_high>Princess Medea: But, you know, he couldn't stop talking about you, <hero>. He really depends on you.
<voice_0x01001CEE><se_high>Princess Medea: Of course, I do too!
<voice_0x01001CEF><se_high>Princess Medea: Ah! If only Prince Charmles were more like you, <hero>!
